release.title: All My Loving
release.disambiguation: THE PARLOPHONE CO. LTD., w/o SOLD IN U.K.

annotation.text:
The first pressing has black label with yellow logo and silver print. “THE PARLOPHONE CO. LTD…” printed at the start of the rim text and the publishing year printed as “recording first published 1963″. 
Matrix numbers: Side 1: 7TCE 790-1N, Side 2: 7TCE 791-1N.
